title: For Sale:  (1945) Astra 600/43 9mm
postcontent: Up for sale is a Spanish Astral 600/43, made in 1945. These weapons were contracted by the German Army and are chambered in the common 9mm parabellum, unlike the originals which were chambered in 9mm Largo. So, ammunition is readily available for this model at Wal-Mart or anywhere that sells ammunition. Few of these weapons ever made It to the Nazis for use, but they have been used in conflicts all over the globe. They are over built and super rugged.
